pizarro 's first expedition , however , turned out to be a failure as his conquistadores , sailing down the pacific coast , reached no farther than colombia before succumbing to such hardships as bad weather , lack of food , and skirmishes with hostile natives , one of which caused almagro to lose an eye by arrow - shot .

